</p>
<IMG SRC=\"../Images/MultiBodyOmc/Shape.png\" ALT=\"model Visualizers.FixedShape2\">
<p>&nbsp;<br>
The dark blue arrows in the figure above are directed along
variable <b>lengthDirection</b>. The light blue arrows are directed
